snippet.title: WHY CAN EVERYONE EXCEPT WHITE PEOPLE BE RACIST????

localized.description: I have all the respect in the world for ALL people! I do not think I'm better than anyone. I love EVERYONE! I love you watching this! Take this video,for what you will. Most of my videos are funny videos, this is just something I felt the need to talk about:) check out my other videos for some fun:)
